== 发行 ==
《0080》最早于1989年3月25日至8月25日在日本以[[VHS|VHS]]和[[激光唱片|激光唱片]]格式分成六集OVA发售<ref name=credits/><ref name=staff/><ref name=crun/>。[[万代影视|万代影视]]曾前后三次重新发售《0080》，第一次是1999年12月18日以两张三集合集版[[DVD|DVD]]发售，DVD第1盘收录第1～3集，第2盘收录第4～6集<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/34386/products/323625/1/ |title=機動戦士ガンダム0080 ポケットの中の戦争 VOLUME1 <nowiki>|</nowiki> アニメーション |website=ORICON NEWS |publisher=[[Oricon|Oricon]] |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190830151706/https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/34386/products/323625/1/ |archive-date=2019-08-30 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-08-30 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/34386/products/323626/1/ |title=機動戦士ガンダム0080 ポケットの中の戦争 VOLUME2 <nowiki>|</nowiki> アニメーション |website=ORICON NEWS |publisher=Oricon |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190830151545/https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/34386/products/323626/1/ |dead-url=no |archivedate=2019-08-30 |access-date=2019-08-30 }}</ref>，之后于2011年4月22日以特价DVD系列“G-Selection”的一部分发售了盒装版DVD<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://na.gundam.info/news/video-music/news_video-music_20110425_69810p.html |title=Limited-edition 'Mobile Suit Gundam 0080' DVD-BOX Now on Sale! <nowiki>|</nowiki> GUNDAM.INFO |date=2011-08-25 |website=GUNDAM.INFO <nowiki>|</nowiki> The official Gundam news and video portal |publisher=Sunrise |language=en-us |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901030307/https://na.gundam.info/news/video-music/news_video-music_20110425_69810p.html |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>，最后于2017年8月29日发售了盒装版蓝光光碟<ref name=crun>{{Cite web |url=https://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2017/04/22-1/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket-gets-first-blu-ray-release-in-august |title="Mobile Suit Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket" Gets First Blu-ray Release in August |last=Komatsu |first=Mikikazu |date=2017-04-22 |website=Crunchyroll |language=en-us |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901030542/https://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2017/04/22-1/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket-gets-first-blu-ray-release-in-august |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。

在北美家庭影院市场最早发售的《0080》由万代娱乐引进，{{le|Animaze|Animaze}}工作室负责配音<ref name=sevakis>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/buried-treasure/2007-08-16 |title=Buried Treasure - Gundam 0080 |last=Sevakis, Justin |date=2007-08-16 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130102012358/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/buried-treasure/2007-08-16 |archive-date=2013-01-02 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。1998年万代首次在北美地区公开<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/1998-08-09/bandai-usa-animevillage.com-announces-tape-layout |title=Bandai USA/AnimeVillage.com Announces Tape Layout |date=1998-08-09 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190830150332/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/1998-08-09/bandai-usa-animevillage.com-announces-tape-layout |archive-date=2019-08-30 |access-date=2019-08-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并最终于1999年3月9日与《[[機動戰士GUNDAM_0083：Stardust_Memory|機動戰士GUNDAM 0083：Stardust Memory]]》一起在VHS套装中发售<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00000IBOD |title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080 & 0083 Box Set – English subtitles [VHS] |website=Amazon.com |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190830150539/https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00000IBOD |archive-date=2019-08-30 |access-date=2019-08-30 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。从1999年9月14日到1999年11月23日，万代又发售了单独作品的三卷版VHS套装，每卷收录两集；12月7日又发售了一套6集版盒装<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00000JSIN | title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080 - War in the Pocket: Episodes 1-2 (English dubbed) [VHS] | website=Amazon.com | accessdate=2019-09-10 | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190910090114/https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00000JSIN | archivedate=2019-09-10 | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00002ND8C | title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080 - War in the Pocket: Truth and Lies (Vol. 3) – Dubbed in English [VHS] | website=Amazon.com | accessdate=2019-09-10 | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190910090154/https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00002ND8C | archivedate=2019-09-10 | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00002NDLK | title=Gundam 0080 - War in the Pocket Boxed Set (Vols. 1-3) [VHS] | website=Amazon.com | accessdate=2019-09-10 | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190910090234/https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00002NDLK | archivedate=2019-09-10 | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2000年12月，万代公布消息将在下一年发售DVD版本的《0080》<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2000-12-02/gundam-news-from-aka-kon |title=Gundam News from AKA KON |date=2000-12-02 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130116224111/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2000-12-02/gundam-news-from-aka-kon |archive-date=2013-01-16 |access-date=2019-08-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是2001年又将原本的10月发售 <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-01-11/bandai-future-releases |title=Bandai future releases |date=January 1, 2001 |website=Anime News Network |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190830150842/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-01-11/bandai-future-releases |archive-date=2019-08-30 |access-date=2019-08-30 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>推迟2002年1月发售，之后更是改为2月<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-09-07/gundam-delays |title=Gundam Delays |date=2001-09-07 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190830150943/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-09-07/gundam-delays |archive-date=2019-08-30 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-08-30 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-10-24/bandai-release-dates |title=Bandai Release Dates |date=2001-10-24 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140131233418/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-10-24/bandai-release-dates |archive-date=2014-01-31 |access-date=2019-08-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最终《0080》的两卷DVD分别于2002年2月19日和4月23日发行<ref name=band-v1>{{cite web | url=http://www.bandai-ent.com:80/products/product_details.cfm?id=43 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20020612005345/http://www.bandai-ent.com/products/product_details.cfm?id=43 | archivedate= 2002-06-12 | title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket (V.1) | publisher=Bandai Entertainment | accessdate= 2018-01-15 | deadurl=yes | df= |language=en}}</ref><ref name=band-v2>{{cite web | url=http://www.bandai-ent.com:80/products/product_details.cfm?id=44 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20020612004635/http://www.bandai-ent.com/products/product_details.cfm?id=44 | archivedate= 2002-06-12 | title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket (V.2) | publisher=Bandai Entertainment | accessdate= 2018-01-15 | deadurl=yes | df= |language=en}}</ref>。在此之后是两套“完整收藏”版的发售：收藏家版本套装于2005年7月12日发售<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.mania.com:80/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-box-set_article_77158.html | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610002641/http://www.mania.com/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-box-set_article_77158.html | archivedate= 2011-06-10 | title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080 Box Set | author=Coulter, Bryce | date=2007-08-03 | website=Mania.com | publisher=Demand Media | accessdate= 2018-01-16 | deadurl=yes | df= |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0009E32SO | title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080 Complete Collection | website=Amazon.com | accessdate=2019-09-10 | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190910090427/https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0009E32SO | archivedate=2019-09-10 | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>，随后于2009年3月23日又以“动画传奇”之名发售了精装版DVD套装<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B001OBBR8S | title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket (Anime Legends Complete Collection) | website=Amazon.com | accessdate=2019-09-10 | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190910090503/https://www.amazon.com/dp/B001OBBR8S | archivedate=2019-09-10 | language=en | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

最初，万代计划2002年在美国[[卡通频道|卡通频道]]上播出《0080》，但日昇却选择将播出时间定在2001年9月<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-08-13/more-gundam-coming-to-tv |title=More Gundam coming to TV |date=August 13, 2001 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901031712/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-08-13/more-gundam-coming-to-tv |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。最终，本片于2001年11月5日开始在卡通频道的[[Toonami|Toonami]]午夜档播出<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-11-01/gundam-0080-on-midnight-run |title=Gundam 0080 on Midnight Run |last=Macdonald |first=Christopher |date=November 1, 2001 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901031845/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-11-01/gundam-0080-on-midnight-run |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。从2003年3月1日开始在“星期六视频娱乐系统”区块播出<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2003-02-17/cartoon-network-pushes-new-programming-block |title=Cartoon Network Pushes New Programming Block |last=Berryhill |first=Garry |date=February 17, 2003 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901032009/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2003-02-17/cartoon-network-pushes-new-programming-block |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。在万代娱乐于2012年停止运营后，该公司也停止了所有的家庭视频放映活动<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-08-31/bandai-entertainment-to-discontinue-home-video-manga-novel-sales |title=Bandai Entertainment to Discontinue Home Video, Manga, Novel Sales (Updated) |date=August 31, 2012 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130116213642/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-08-31/bandai-entertainment-to-discontinue-home-video-manga-novel-sales |archive-date=2013-01-16 |access-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年7月，{{le|Right Stuf|Right Stuf Inc.}}宣布将于2016年底与日昇合作发行DVD动画<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-07-01/right-stuf-announces-gundam-0083-afterglow-of-zeon-galaxy-angel-more-gundam-license-rescues/.103837 |title=Right Stuf Announces Gundam 0083 Afterglow of Zeon, Galaxy Angel, More Gundam License Rescues |last=Ressler |first=Karen |date=July 1, 2016 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901032248/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-07-01/right-stuf-announces-gundam-0083-afterglow-of-zeon-galaxy-angel-more-gundam-license-rescues/.103837 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。一个月后又公布消息将时间推迟到2017年初<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-08-13/right-stuf-to-release-turn-a-gundam-tv-anime-on-blu-ray-disc/.105331 |title=Right Stuf to Release Turn A Gundam TV Anime on Blu-ray Disc |last=Hodgkins |first=Crystalyn |date=August 13, 2016 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901032601/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-08-13/right-stuf-to-release-turn-a-gundam-tv-anime-on-blu-ray-disc/.105331 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。最终两家合作于2017年1月3日开始重新发售《0080》的动画<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-01-03/north-american-anime-manga-releases-january-1-7/.110594 |title=North American Anime, Manga Releases, January 1-7 |date=January 3, 2017 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190830152641/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-01-03/north-american-anime-manga-releases-january-1-7/.110594 |archive-date=2019-08-30 |access-date=2019-08-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2016-10-06/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket-coming-january-2017-from-right-stuf-inc-and-sunrise-inc/.107347 |title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080 War in the Pocket Coming January 2017 from Right Stuf, Inc. and Sunrise Inc. |date=2016-10-06 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190830152344/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2016-10-06/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket-coming-january-2017-from-right-stuf-inc-and-sunrise-inc/.107347 |archive-date=2019-08-30 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-08-30 }}</ref>。

==相关作品==
===印刷制品===

目前已经制作发行了大量关于《0080》的书籍。由望月勇太郎编写并由Studio Hard负责插图制作的[[游戏书|游戏手册]]《机动战士高达0080 消失的高达NT》（{{lang-ja|機動戦士ガンダム0080 消えたガンダムNT}}）已由万代于1989年3月20日发行<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4891890126 |title=機動戦士 ガンダム0080(ダブルオーエィティ)―消えたガンダムNT(ニュータイプ) (バンダイ文庫―ゲームブックシリーズ) |website=Amazon.co.jp |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901061626/https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4891890126 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}<p>{{cite web | url=http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0015174403 | title=機動戦士　ガンダム００８０ 消えたガンダムNT | website=BookOffOnline.co.jp | accessdate=2019-09-01 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190901032918/http://www.bookoffonline.co.jp/old/0015174403 | archivedate=2019-09-01 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。基于动画改编的小说《{{nihongo|克莉丝所梦见的|クリスが見る夢}}》{{refnest|group="注释"|部分来源翻译为《梦见克莉丝》<ref name=sina20170427>{{Cite web |title=《机动战士高达0080》将推出高清重制版Blu-ray Box |url=http://comic.sina.com.cn/dongman/2017-04-27/doc-ifyetwtf8475953.shtml |accessdate=2019-09-12 |date=2017-04-27 |work=comic.sina.com.cn |language=zh-cn |archiveurl=https://archive.fo/ALQjb#selection-869.68-869.71 |archivedate=2019-09-12}}</ref>}}由山贺博之撰写并由美树本晴彦和窪岡俊之进行插图设计。作为特别制作刊登在[[德间书店|德间书店]]的《[[Animage|Animage]]》杂志1989年4月刊上<ref name=crun/>。1989年4月至1989年8月，{{link-ja|池原成利|池原しげと}}在[[讲谈社|讲谈社]]旗下[[漫画杂志|漫画杂志]]《[[Comic_BomBom|Comic BomBom]]》连载了同名漫画<ref name=kpc>{{Cite web |url=http://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?item=0000221444 |title=機動戦士ガンダム００８０　ポケットの中の戦争 |website=kc.kodansha.co.jp |publisher=Kodansha |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901063842/http://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?item=0000221444 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。之后，讲谈社将他们集结成[[单行本|单行本]]于1989年7月17日首次发行<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp/mg/books/1163194 |title=機動戦士ガンダム0080(講談社コミックスボンボン) |website=mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp |publisher=Agency for Cultural Affairs |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901063547/https://mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp/mg/books/1163194 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>，并于2003年8月18日以“白金漫画”之名再度发行<ref name=kpc/>，于2006年以KC Delux系列再版<ref>{{cite web | url=http://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?isbn=9784063722215 | title=機動戦士ガンダム００８０　ポケットの中の戦争 | publisher=Kodansha | accessdate=2019-09-10 | language=ja | archive-url=https://archive.today/20190910090903/http://kc.kodansha.co.jp/product?item=0000222812 | archive-date=2019-09-10 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。1989年7月开始，万代旗下杂志《{{link-ja|B-CLUB|B-CLUB (模型雑誌)}}》出版了两卷“视觉漫画”改编版《VISUAL COMIC 机动战士高达0080》（{{lang-ja|VISUAL COMIC 機動戦士ガンダム0080}}）<ref>{{cite web | url=https://mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp/mg/books/1163003 | title=機動戦士ガンダム0080(B-club visual comic)vol.1 | website=Media Arts Database | publisher=Agency for Cultural Affairs | accessdate=2019-09-10 | language=ja | archive-url=https://archive.today/20190910091905/https://mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp/mg/books/1163003 | archive-date=2019-09-10 | dead-url=no }}<p>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4891890355 | title=機動戦士ガンダム0080―ポケットの中の戦争 (Vol.1) (B‐club visual comic) | website=Amazon.co.jp | accessdate=2019-09-11 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190911011404/https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4891890355 | archivedate=2019-09-11 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。日本[[文部科学省|文部科学省]][[文化厅|文化厅]]的媒体艺术数据库和[[亞馬遜日本|Amazon.co.jp]]都确认了这个发布日期，但它们提供的第二卷发售日期却各不相同：前者登记的信息为1989年10月<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp/mg/books/1163004 |title=機動戦士ガンダム0080(B-club visual comic)vol.2 |website=Media Arts Database |publisher=Agency for Cultural Affairs |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190911004305/https://mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp/mg/books/1163004 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |access-date=2019-09-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而后者展示的发售时间则是1989年9月<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4891890479 |title=機動戦士ガンダム0080―ポケットの中の戦争 (Vol.2) (B‐club visual comic) |date=2019-09-11 |website=Amazon.co.jp |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190911004451/https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4891890479 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |access-date=2019-09-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由《0080》的动画故事构成結城恭介撰写的同名{{le|小说化|novelization|小说}}由[[角川书店|角川书店]]于1989年10月出版，封面插图和插图由美树本晴彦负责<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4044111014 |title=機動戦士ガンダム0080 ポケットの中の戦争 (角川文庫―スニーカー文庫) |website=Amazon.co.jp |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190911004608/https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4044111014 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |access-date=2019-09-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。作为《MS Saga 机动战士高达漫画选集》（MS Saga – Mobile Suit Gundam in Comic）的一部分，[[MediaWorks|MediaWorks]]于1994年2月1日出版了一部由{{link-ja|水原贤治|水原賢治}}绘制的短篇漫画《口袋里的战争》（{{lang-ja|ポケットの中の戦争}}）<ref>{{cite web | url=https://mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp/mg/books/1270500 | title=MS SAGA(機動戦士ガンダムコミックアンソロジー)vol.4 | website=Media Arts Database | publisher=Agency for Cultural Affairs | accessdate=2019-09-11 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190911010824/https://mediaarts-db.bunka.go.jp/mg/books/1270500 | archivedate=2019-09-11 | dead-url=no }}<p>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4073007599 | title=MS Saga―Mobile suit Gundam in comic (Vol.4) | website=Amazon.co.jp | accessdate=2019-09-11 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190911010737/https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4073007599 | archivedate=2019-09-11 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-ja|旭屋书店|旭屋書店|旭屋出版}}于1998年6月到7月发行了两部名为《机动战士高达0080 OVA电影》（Mobile Suit Gundam 0080 the OVA Movies）的电影漫画<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/book/475110130/ | title=Mobile Suit Gundam0080 the OVA Movies I | publisher=Oricon | accessdate=2019-09-11 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190911010714/https://www.oricon.co.jp/book/475110130/ | archivedate=2019-09-11 | dead-url=no }}<p>{{cite web | url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/book/475110131/ | title=Mobile Suit Gundam0080 the OVA Movies II | publisher=Oricon | accessdate=2019-09-11 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190911010616/https://www.oricon.co.jp/book/475110131/ | archivedate=2019-09-11 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4751101307 | title=機動戦士ガンダム0080・ポケットの中の戦争―オリジナル・アニメ・ビデオ・フィルムコミック (1) (旭屋出版コミックス) | website=Amazon.co.jp | accessdate=2019-09-11 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190911010526/https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4751101307 | archivedate=2019-09-11 | dead-url=no }}<p>{{cite web | url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4751101315/ | title=機動戦士ガンダム0080・ポケットの中の戦争―オリジナル・アニメ・ビデオ・フィルムコミック (2) (旭屋出版コミックス) | website=Amazon.co.jp | accessdate=2019-09-11 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190911010345/https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4751101315/ | archivedate=2019-09-11 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2022年2月26日，制作方又发售了一部名为《机动战士GUNDAM 口袋里的战争》（{{Lang|ja|機動戦士ガンダム　ポケットの中の戦争}}）<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-02-20 |title= |script-title=ja:今週の新刊：「機動戦士ガンダムSEED」公式外伝「ECLIPSE」 「とある科学の超電磁砲」も |url=https://mantan-web.jp/article/20220218dog00m200096000c.html |website=MANTANWEB（まんたんウェブ） |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.vn/ZuYJP |archive-date=2022-06-16 |access-date=2022-06-16}}</ref>。

===音响制品===

《0080》的音乐部分由{{link-ja|橿渕哲郎|かしぶち哲郎}}创作<ref name=staff/>。由{{link-ja|椎名惠|椎名恵}}所演绎的两支歌曲被分别用作本剧的片头主题曲《{{nihongo|有一天会到达天空|いつか空に届いて}}》和片尾主题曲《{{nihongo|遥远的记忆|遠い記憶}}》<ref name=staff/><ref>{{Cite web |title=椎名恵「『今夜はANGEL』デビュー直後は謎のシンガーだった」 |url=https://smart-flash.jp/entame/26308 |accessdate=2019-09-13 |date=2017-10-02 |work=Smart FLASH[光文社週刊誌]スマフラ／スマートフラッシュ |language=ja |archiveurl=https://archive.fo/ZjYZp |archivedate=2019-09-13}}</ref>。包含剧中的器乐和声乐的两张[[原声音乐|原声]]专辑于1999年3月5日由[[King_Records|King Records]]以《Sound Sketch I》和《II》之名发行<ref name=cds>{{cite web | url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/237769/products/133840/1/ | title=機動戦士ガンダム 0080 ポケットの中の戦争 Sound Sketch I | publisher=Oricon | accessdate=2019-09-11 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190911011148/https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/237769/products/133840/1/ | archivedate=2019-09-11 | dead-url=no }}<p>{{cite web | url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/133585/products/133841/1/ | title=機動戦士ガンダム 0080 ポケットの中の戦争 Sound Sketch II | publisher=Oricon | accessdate=2019-09-11 | language=ja | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190911011241/https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/133585/products/133841/1/ | archivedate=2019-09-11 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。前一张原声专辑包含17首曲子，第二张则收录了14支曲子<ref name=cds/>。大部分声乐歌曲由椎名惠和林原惠美负责演绎<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://www.ex.org:80/5.1/41-cd_gundam.html | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20010707093313/http://www.ex.org/5.1/41-cd_gundam.html | archivedate=2001-07-07 | title=Gundam 0080 Sound Sketch 2 | author=McCarter, Charles | date=2000-02-03<!-- http://web.archive.org/web/20010620055656/http://www.ex.org:80/5.1/ --> | journal=EX | publisher=Society for the Promotion of Japanese Animation | volume=5 | issue=1 | deadurl=yes | df= |language=en}}</ref>。本剧中的歌曲也被收录进一些高达系列音乐汇编集中，包括《GUN-{}-DAM SINGLES HISTORY》和《GUN-{}-DAM 30th ANNIVERSARY GUN-{}-DAM SONGS 145》<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cdjournal.com/main/news/-/27612 |title=ガンダムソング全145曲入り！スペシャルCD-BOXの詳細が明らかに - CDJournal ニュース |date=2009-11-26 |website=www.cdjournal.com |publisher=Ongaku Shuppansha |language=ja |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901040117/https://www.cdjournal.com/main/news/-/27612 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。

==评价和影响==

===评价和排名===

《0080》获得了评论家的广泛赞誉。[[动画新闻网|动画新闻网]]的賈斯汀·賽瓦基斯（Justin Sevakis）称其为“有史以来最激动人心的战争故事之一”<ref name=sevakis/>。同一网站的劳伦·奥西尼（Lauren Orsini）给了《0080》的字幕版评分为A，而给配音版则是B-的评分，称赞它的“信息强有力”，并说这个“短小而沉重的情感故事”是“和〈[[機動戰士GUNDAM|高达]]〉一样的具有人性光辉的”<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/mobile-suit-gundam-0080/war-in-the-pocket/complete-collection/.113348 |title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket DVD |last=Orsini |first=Lauren |date=2017-03-13 |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |access-date=2019-09-01 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20170313144420/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/mobile-suit-gundam-0080/war-in-the-pocket/complete-collection/.113348 |archive-date=2017-03-13 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。RevolutionSF网站的凯文·佩扎诺（Kevin Pezzano）将《0080》评为9分（满分10分），并极力称赞本剧“严肃的故事情节”和“梦幻般的动画”<ref>{{cite web |last1=Pezzano |first1=Kevin |title=Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket {{ndash}} Review |url=http://www.revolutionsf.com/article.php?id=648 |website=RevolutionSF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091223062201/http://www.revolutionsf.com/article.php?id=648 |archivedate=2009-12-23 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2019-04-04 |language=en }}</ref>。《The Cart Driver》称《0080》为“毫无疑问是我所观赏过的最棒的高达作品”、“可能除了《[[FLCL|FLCL]]》，这部剧是我见过的最好的短篇OVA”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://thecartdriver.com/secret-santa-review-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket/ |title=Secret Santa review: Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket |last=Scamp |date=2012-12-22 |website=The Cart Driver |language=en-US |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901060450/http://thecartdriver.com/secret-santa-review-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket/ |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。

《The Fandom Post》的Chris Beveridge给了《0080》一个A-的评分，并说明道“这部剧的故事和动画经历了时间的考验”而其中的角色更是“令人触手可及”，从而得出结论为“强烈推荐”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fandompost.com/2016/12/22/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket-anime-dvd-review/ |title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080 War In the Pocket Anime DVD Review |last=Beveridge |first=Chris |date=2016-12-22 |website=The Fandom Post |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901060719/https://www.fandompost.com/2016/12/22/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket-anime-dvd-review/ |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 |language=en }}</ref>。《{{le|Otaku USA|Otaku USA}}》的Evan Minto给予本剧“推荐”评级，同时称《0080》为“高达原本应有的样子”，并声称它是“在一个被撕成两半的世界中失去纯真的短暂而凄美的故事，并且有效地证明了在战争中，所有人都是受害者”<ref name=otaku/>。[[福布斯|福布斯]]的奥利·巴尔德（Ollie Barder）称其为“令人心碎的杰作”和“对高达迷人世界的一个很好的介绍”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/olliebarder/2017/04/21/gundam-0080-dvd-review-a-heartbreaking-masterpiece/ |title='Gundam 0080' DVD Review: A Heartbreaking Masterpiece |last=Barder |first=Ollie |date=2017-04-21 |website=Forbes |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901060920/https://www.forbes.com/ |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。Nefarious评论给《0080》的评分为“高”并评论道这是“一个有着令人满意的结局的独立好故事”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://nefariousreviews.com/2019/01/14/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket-anime-review/ |title=Mobile Suit Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket – Anime Review |last=Reviews |first=Nefarious |date=2019-01-14 |website=Nefarious Reviews |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901061110/https://nefariousreviews.com/2019/01/14/mobile-suit-gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket-anime-review/ |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。{{le|Micah Wright|Micah Wright}}在2002年将《0080》列为他最喜爱的动画系列之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2002-06-11/cowboy-bebop-rated-in-top-10-at-toon-zone |title=Cowboy Bebop rated in Top 10 at Toon Zone |date=2002-06-11 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120718235247/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2002-06-11/cowboy-bebop-rated-in-top-10-at-toon-zone |archive-date=2012-07-18 |access-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《0080》于2011年重新发布的DVD盒装版，于2002年4月18日至24日获[[Oricon|Oricon]]最佳动画片畅销DVD排行榜第三，总计售出3,739张<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-04-26/japan-animation-dvd-ranking-april-18-24-part-1 |title=Japan's Animation DVD Ranking, April 18-24 (Part 1) |last=Loo |first=Egan |date=2011-04-26 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901062653/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-04-26/japan-animation-dvd-ranking-april-18-24-part-1 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。2017年重新发售的蓝光套装销量为6,352份，在Oricon的动画蓝光光碟销量排行榜中排名第三<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-09-05/japan-animation-blu-ray-disc-ranking-august-28-september-3/.120957 |title=Japan's Animation Blu-ray Disc Ranking, August 28-September 3 |last=Loo |first=Egan |date=September 5, 2017 |website=Anime News Network |language=en |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190901062441/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-09-05/japan-animation-blu-ray-disc-ranking-august-28-september-3/.120957 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-09-01 }}</ref>。在第一集发售后的1989年4月，《Newtype》杂志采访了首次没有参与高达系列作品制作的富野由悠季。他称赞了《0080》导演努力使这部作品变得更切合实际，并首次尝试将目光转向除了机动战士之间的战斗以外的事情<ref name=sevakis/>。

===影响===
2017年开始放映的[[ONA|网络小说动画]]《[[機動戰士GUNDAM_Twilight_AXIS|機動戰士GUNDAM Twilight AXIS]]》中出场的主角[[机动战士|机动战士]]“崔斯坦”被设定为《0080》中出场的机体“阿历克斯”的修改版<ref name="アニメ回顧録"/>。

